PicturePay from Allied Payment enables financial institutions' customers to pay their bills simply by taking a picture of the bill with their smartphone. PicturePay drives bill pay adoption using a simple technology that customers already know and trust.


 


PicturePay streamlines the process and eliminates the need for a keyboard by completing the data entry for the user. Using PicturePay, you eliminate the hassle of entering the payee and account information online.




Photo Bill Pay




Expedite payments




PicturePay gives users the option to expedite payments for a small convenience fee. This eliminates more expensive late fees for customers and generates additional revenue for the institution.


 


PicturePay users also tend to have higher account balances than others. With a 99.4% read rate, PicturePay gives users a convenient and trustworthy option to pay their bills using only their smartphone.





