TellerPay from Allied Payment is a walk-up payment solution that allows financial institutions to easily accept and process over-the-counter payments in the branch.


 


This increases the value of the branch by allowing customers to manage more business at a single location. TellerPay drives efficiency by seamlessly integrating with the institution's intranet. This allows tellers to instantly process the payment.




Over-The-Counter Bill Pay




