With PortalPay from Allied Payment, customers can make loan payments from their internal or external accounts via the institution's website. PortalPay operates as a landing page within an institution's website where the user can simply enter contact information, bank account information, and loan information.


 


This is a convenient method for internal departments such as collections or customer service to collect payments from external accounts.




Web Loan Payments




Enhance customer experience




This simple and convenient process will enhance customer experience. It will also extend web reach and can support customer acquisition by enabling loan payments from nonmembers and customers.


 


Allied Payment is an industry leader in the field. Our goal is to make the bill paying process easier and more convenient for customers, and more efficient and cost-effective for financial institutions.









Simple Loan Payments with PortalPay




