Company Overview of Allied Payment Network, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Allied Payment Network, Inc. provides online bill payment services to financial institutions and consumers. Its products and services include PicturePay that enables financial institutions' customers to pay their bills by taking a picture of the bill with their smartphone; FlexPay, an Internet bill pay solution; and BizPay, a small business payment solution that allows financial institutions to pursue small business banking relationships. The company also provides PortalPay that enables customers to make loan payments from their internal or external accounts via the institution's website; and TellerPay, a walk-up payment solution that allows financial institutions to accept and process over-...
Allied Payment Network, Inc. provides online bill payment services to financial institutions and consumers. Its products and services include PicturePay that enables financial institutions' customers to pay their bills by taking a picture of the bill with their smartphone; FlexPay, an Internet bill pay solution; and BizPay, a small business payment solution that allows financial institutions to pursue small business banking relationships. The company also provides PortalPay that enables customers to make loan payments from their internal or external accounts via the institution's website; and TellerPay, a walk-up payment solution that allows financial institutions to accept and process over-the-counter payments in the branch. It serves community banks, credit unions, and partner networks. Allied Payment Network, Inc. was founded in 2010 and is based in Fort Wayne, Indiana.
